---
title: Crumbed Fish & Lemony Roast Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt & Slivered Almonds
description: A golden and crunchy crumb on fish is the only way to eat fish. It matches the bright and sunny couscous, tossed with roast veggies and there’s a zap of zest in this bowl too. Everything is shining and golden tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crumbed-chicken-lemony-roast-veggie-couscous-44011b67.jpg
